subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: What could have been one of the biggest upsets in tennis history turned instead into a 6-7 (5), 7-6 (1), 5-7, 6-1, 10-8 victory for Roger Federer, the world’s longstanding No. 1 player.
